TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PERIOD_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT, DECODE(GFV.NEW_BUSINESSUNITMAP, 64, 'SGPAFA', OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT) as TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, DECODE(GFV.NEW_POSITIONSEQ, NULL, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_POSITIONSEQ, GFV.NEW_POSITIONSEQ) as DEC_POSITIONSEQ, DECODE(GFV.NEW_PAYEESEQ, NULL, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ, GFV.NEW_PAYEESEQ) as DEC_PAYEESEQ, DECODE(GFV.NEW_POSITIONNAME, NULL, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_POSITION_NAME, GFV.NEW_POSITIONNAME) as TXT_POSITION_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENT_AMOUNT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_EARNING_GROUP, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_UPDATE, CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE2, DECODE(CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3, NULL, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3) GENERICATTRIBUTE3, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE4, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE5, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE6, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE7, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE8, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICBOOLEAN2, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_TXN_DESCRIPTION, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_AGENT_STATUS, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_NRIC, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_BENEF_AMOUNT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_BANKCODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_BRANCHCODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNUMBER, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_COMPANY_CODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_INTERM_SWIFTCODE FROM OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL inner join CS_PARTICIPANT CS_PARTICIPANT on CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ = OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ AND CS_PARTICIPANT.REMOVEDATE > SYSDATE inner join IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLEDATE on OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE = TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE <= TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL' inner join IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLETYPE on OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE = IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_VALUE AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_PAYMENT_CYCLE_TYPE' AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_FILE_NAME = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' left outer join VW_OUT_GL_FA_ORI_AGENT GFV on OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT = GFV.PROCESSINGUNITNAME AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_POSITION_NAME = GFV.ORI_POSITIONNAME AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_POSITIONSEQ = GFV.ORI_POSITIONSEQ WHERE ((OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Settlment_Way = 'GIRO' AND NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Agent_Status, '00') <> '70') OR (NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY, 'UNPAID') = 'GIRO' AND NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Agent_Status, '00') = '70')) AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND DECODE(GFV.NEW_BUSINESSUNITMAP, 64, 'SGPAFA', OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT) in ($$STR_BUSINESS_UNIT) AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ NOT IN (SELECT DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ FROM OUT_PAYMENT_RESULT_TRACE WHERE TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE') AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY = '$$STR_SGD' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.txt_Remarks is null union all SELECT 0 as DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ, comppay.CYCLEDATE as DTE_CYCLE_DATE, comppay.CYCLETYPE as TXT_CYCLE_TYPE, comppay.PERIODNAME as TXT_PERIOD_NAME, comppay.PROCESSINGUNITNAME as TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT, --comppay.BUSINESSUNITNAME as TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, 'AFA CHANNEL' as TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, 0 as DEC_POSITIONSEQ, 0 as DEC_PAYEESEQ, --payee.payeeid as TXT_POSITION_NAME, 'SGYAIAFA' as TXT_POSITION_NAME, comppay.PAYMENT as DEC_PAYMENT_AMOUNT, comppay.PAYMENTCURRENCY as TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY, comppay.EARNINGGROUP as TXT_EARNING_GROUP, comppay.status as TXT_STATUS, comppay.UPDATEDATE as DTE_UPDATE, 0 as PAYEESEQ, '' as LASTNAME, '' as GENERICATTRIBUTE1, '' as GENERICATTRIBUTE2, par.genericattribute3 as GENERICATTRIBUTE3, '' as GENERICATTRIBUTE4, '' as GENERICATTRIBUTE5, par.genericattribute6 as GENERICATTRIBUTE6, par.genericattribute7 as GENERICATTRIBUTE7, par.genericattribute8 as GENERICATTRIBUTE8, 0 as GENERICBOOLEAN2, '' as TXT_TXN_DESCRIPTION, '' as TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD, '' as TXT_AGENT_STATUS, '' as TXT_BENEF_NRIC, '' as TXT_BENEF_NAME, null as DEC_BENEF_AMOUNT, '' as TXT_BENEF_BANKCODE, '' as TXT_BENEF_BRANCHCODE, '' as TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNUMBER, '' as TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNAME, '' as TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY, '' as TXT_BENEF_COMPANY_CODE, '' as TXT_INTERM_SWIFTCODE FROM OUT_PAYMENT_FA_COMP comppay inner join in_etl_control IN_CYCLETYPE on comppay.CYCLETYPE=IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_VALUE and IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'PAYMENT_CYCLE_TYPE' AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'AGY_PU' inner join in_etl_control IN_CYCLEDATE on comppay.CYCLEDATE=TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL' inner join cs_payee payee on 1 = 1 and payee.payeeid = 'AFA Channel' and payee.removedate = to_date('22000101','yyyymmdd') and payee.islast = 1 inner join cs_participant par on payee.payeeseq = par.payeeseq and par.removedate = to_date('22000101','yyyymmdd') and par.islast = 1 where comppay.PAYMENT>0 and 'FACMP' in ($$STR_BUSINESS_UNIT) and comppay.batchnum in ( select max(B.BATCHNUM) from OUT_GL_BATCH B , IN_ETL_CONTROL L where B.CYCLEDATE = comppay.CYCLEDATE AND STATUS='COMPLETED' AND processingunitname ='$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND L.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_MAX_CYCLE_DATE' AND L.TXT_FILE_NAME = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND (B.ISLATEST ='Y' OR NVL(L.DEC_ENFORCE_FLG, 0)=1) )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
--change by Ada 20140627, for FSD required beneficary name 20len --IIF(TXT_AGENT_STATUS='70',TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNAME,GA3_BENEFICIARY_NAME)
substr(IIF(TXT_AGENT_STATUS='70',TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNAME,GA3_BENEFICIARY_NAME),1,20)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_BENEFICIARY_NAME
O_ORDERING_PARTY_NAME
O_TXN_TYPE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(TXT_DEBIT_ACCT_COUNTRY_CD),ABORT('Can not find the debit account country code for GIRO File'),TXT_DEBIT_ACCT_COUNTRY_CD)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_DEBIT_ACCT_COUNTRY_CD

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: iif(isnull(TXT_DEBIT_ACCT_NUMBER),ABORT('Can not find the debit account number for GIRO File'),TXT_DEBIT_ACCT_NUMBER)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_DEBIT_ACCT_NUMBER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
((not isnull(GENERICATTRIBUTE5)) and UPPER(GENERICATTRIBUTE5) ='BANK' AND TXT_EARNING_GROUP='SGD' AND (NOT ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE6)) AND (NOT ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE7)) AND (NOT ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE8)))
OR
( TXT_AGENT_STATUS='70' AND (NOT ISNULL(TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY) ) AND TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY='GIRO')
OR
(UPPER(TXT_POSITION_NAME)='SGYAIAFA')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: TXT_CMP_CD = IN_CMP_CD AND TXT_SETTLEMENT_WAY = IN_SETTLEMENT_WAY AND DTE_EFFECTIVE_START <= IN_CYCLE_DATE AND DTE_EFFECTIVE_END > IN_CYCLE_DATE AND TXT_CURRENCY_CD = IN_CURRENCY_CODE
